snippet.title: Barbie horse adventure riding camp ds review
snippet.description:
In this video I review Barbie horse adventure riding camp for the Nintendo ds! In this video, I show some gameplay and features of Barbie horse adventure riding camp. There isn't much to do in the game, but the game is good for younger girls to play every once in a while.
